description: The investment seeks to track the investment results of the Bloomberg 2021 Term High Yield and Income Index. The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index, and may invest up to 10% of its assets in certain futures, options and swap contracts, cash and cash equivalents. The underlying index is composed of U.S. dollar-denominated, taxable, fixed-rate, high yield and BBB or equivalently rated corporate bonds scheduled to mature between January 1, 2021 and December 15, 2021, inclusive. The fund is non-diversified.
name: iShares iBonds 2021 Term High Yield and Income ETF
